title: Midnight In The Desert 02-24-2016 FS - Sasquatch Genome
description:
Midnight In The Desert show from February 24th, 2016 titled "The Sasquatch Genome 

Project".

Host: Heather Wade

Guest: Dr Melba Ketchum

Topic: The Sasquatch Genome Project

ABR: 64 kbps, ASR: 22 khz, Channels: 2, Codec: MP3

No adverts. Includes bumper music, sounders and show plugs.



Note: There is a 90 second dropout after the bottom of hour 3.

This is a studio/production snafu which dropped the Midnight In The Desert audio 

feed and inserted music.

The dropout was shortened and a brief tone inserted to mark the location
